      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i just got this crazy headache out of nowhere. like, the worst one i've ever had. it's super intense and i noticed my left cheek feels kinda weird and heavy and like it's drooping a bit? i get migraines sometimes so i'm thinking it might just be a really bad one. what do u think?",
